2BDELETE%20on%20%26quot%3Bdiversity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELegally%2C%20companies%20have%20to%20disclose%20some%20information%20about%20their%20workforces%20in%20their%20annual%20reports%2C%20such%20as%20how%20many%20people%20work%20for%20them%2C%20but%20they're%20not%20required%20to%20say%20anything%20about%20diversity%20and%20demographics.%20It%20had%20become%20popular%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20or%20so%20for%20companies%20to%20make%20such%20disclosures%20anyway%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20George%20Floyd's%20murder%20in%202020.%20But%20that's%20shifted%20as%20companies%20have%20become%20increasingly%20worried%20about%20being%20viewed%20as%20%26quot%3Bwoke%26quot%3B%20or%20overly%20progressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Motors%2C%20for%20example%2C%20cut%20the%20DEI%20section%20of%20its%20annual%20report.%20In%20its%202023%20report%2C%20the%20automaker%20said%20it%20aimed%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20inclusive%20company%20in%20the%20world%26quot%3B%20and%20touted%20its%20diverse%20board%20of%20directors%20and%20dozen%20employee%20resource%20groups.%20In%20its%202024%20report%2C%20that%20section%20was%20gone.%20PepsiCo's%20latest%20filing%20scrapped%20a%20breakdown%20of%20its%20workforce%20demographics%20as%20well%20as%20a%20line%20about%20how%20it%20believed%20its%20%26quot%3Bculture%20of%20diversity%2C%20equity%20and%20inclusion%20is%20a%20competitive%20advantage%20that%20fuels%20innovation%2C%20enhances%20our%20ability%20to%20attract%20and%20retain%20talent%20and%20strengthens%20our%20reputation.%26quot%3B%20The%20soda%20maker%20did%2C%20however%2C%20retain%20a%20mention%20of%20pay%20equity.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-is-latest-company-to-shake-up-dei-initiatives-memo-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDisney%20shortened%20its%20DEI%20section%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20part%20removing%20mentions%20of%20employee%20development%20programs%20and%20fellowships%20for%20underrepresented%20talent%20w