0landing%20a%20role%20with%20a%20three-year%20gap%20and%20being%20close%20to%20retirement%20age%20would%20be%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20wasn't%20familiar%20with%20the%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-companies-hiring-job-openings-ai-cloud-infrastructure-layoffs-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehiring%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20online%20interviews%2C%20and%20there%20weren't%20many%20administrative%20assistant%20roles%20remotely%20or%20in%20her%20area.%20The%20available%20ones%20had%20hundreds%20of%20applicants.%20And%20because%20she%20switched%20industries%20during%20her%20career%2C%20she%20said%20she%20couldn't%20prove%20her%20authority%20in%20one%20field%20as%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeterson%20landed%20a%20job%20at%20a%20library%20a%20month%20ago%2C%20which%20pays%20%2411%20an%20hour%2C%20but%20she%20injured%20her%20ankle%20two%20weeks%20in%20and%20said%20she's%20applying%20elsewhere.%20She%20doesn't%20foresee%20herself%20being%20able%20to%20retire%20as%20she%20relies%20on%20her%20%241%2C600%20monthly%20Social%20Security%20checks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20trying%20to%20save%20as%20much%20as%20I%20can%20and%20finally%20put%20myself%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsole-breadwinner-single-income-family-budget-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebudget%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20my%20main%20concern%20now%20is%20my%20mom%2C%20who's%20losing%20her%20memory%20and%20eyesight%20but%20doesn't%20want%20to%20go%20into%20assisted%20living%2C%26quot%3B%20Peterson%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20to%20stay%20motivated%20when%20you%20feel%20like%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20skills%20or%20face%20age%20discrimination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20labor%20market%20has%20been%20difficult%20for%20job%20seekers%20in%20general%2C%20including%20for%20older%20Americans%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20have%20taken%20huge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstruggling-job-seekers-pay-cuts-cant-retire-unemployment-social-security-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epay%20cuts%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20a%20layoff%20or%20voluntary%20departure.%20Additionally%2C%20even%20though%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20is%20historically%20low%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffred.stlouisfed.org%2Fseries%2FJTSHIR%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehiring%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20slipped%20from%20more%20than%204%25%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20to%203.3%25%20and%203.4%25%20in%20recent%20months.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERita%20Choula%2C%20senior%20director%20of%20caregiving%20for%20AARP%20Public%20Policy%20Institute%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20more%20companies%20should%20aim%20to%20support%20caregivers.%20This%20can%20look%20like%20offering%20leave%20for%20caregivers%20or%20changes%20to%20company%20culture%20to%20normalize%20caring%20for%20an%20older%20adult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20great%20that%20you%20have%20vacation%20leave%2C%20but%20we%20really%20want%20caregivers%20who%20are%20under%20enough%20stress%20to%20be%20able%20to%20take%20that%20time%20for%20them%20to%20rest%20and%20reset%2C%26quot%3B%20Choula%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2256a548af-38da-48bb-9c25-05a2ca2924e3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOnly%20finding%20limited%20work%20options%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOlder%20Americans%20told%20BI%20that%20caregiving%20meant%20sacrificing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmba-graduates-cant-find-jobs-white-collar-hiring-slowdown-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecareer%20opportunities%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20didn't%20work%20with%20their%20schedules%2C%20often%20adversely%20affecting%20their%20finances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20employed%20caregivers%20face%20strain%20in%20managing%20both%20caregiving%20and%20work%20responsibilities%20simultaneously%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20AARP%20report%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20consequences%20can%20lead%20to%20reduced%20job%20security%2C%2