cement-live-updates-royal-challengers-bengaluru-mens-team-captain-for-ipl-2025-live-virat-kohli-rajat-patidar-krunal-pandya-7698842%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20Captaincy%20Announcement%20Highlights%3A%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20have%20announced%20batter%20Rajat%20Patidar%20as%20their%20new%20captain%20for%20the%202025%20edition%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Union%20Budget%202025%3A%20Balancing%20Act%20Or%20Missed%20Opportunity%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20headlines%20proclaimed%20a%20feel-good%20budget.%20Taxpayers%20would%20now%20be%20exempted%20their%20first%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20of%20income%2C%20putting%20a%20lot%20more%20money%20in%20their%20pockets.%20The%20government%2C%20the%20quick-take%20claimed%2C%20had%20come%20up%20with%20a%20winner%3A%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbudget%20for%20the%20middle-class%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20was%20that%20the%20whole%20story%3F%20With%20rising%20unemployment%2C%20a%20growing%20budget%20deficit%2C%20and%20urgent%20demands%20for%20better%20social%20welfare%2C%20the%20Finance%20Minister's%20Union%20Budget%202025%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20issues%20it%20needed%20to%20address.%20Seen%20in%20that%20light%2C%20this%20Budget%20is%20a%20glaring%20missed%20opportunity%E2%80%94cautious%20where%20boldness%20was%20needed%2C%20indifferent%20where%20urgency%20was%20demanded.%20The%20stock-market's%20reaction%20says%20it%20all%3A%20the%20Budget%20has%20failed%20to%20inspire%20confidence%20or%20address%20the%20pressing%20realities%20of%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Never-Ending%20Jobs%20Crisis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unemployment%20crisis%20simply%20has%20not%20been%20addressed.%20While%20the%20tax%20break%20offers%20some%20relief%20to%20the%20employed%2C%20it%20is%20striking%20that%20the%20Budget%20extends%20no%20support%20to%20those%20who%20do%20not%20qualify%20for%20it%E2%80%94not%20because%20they%20earn%20too%20much%2C%20but%20because%20they%20earn%20nothing%20at%20all.%20This%20paradox%20becomes%20even%20starker%20when%20one%20considers%20that%20the%20Employment%20Linked%20Incentive%2C%20which%20was%20announced%20last%20year%20as%20the%20core%20pillar%20of%20the%20government's%20employment%20policy%2C%20saw%20its%20budget%20slashed%20from%20Rs.10%2C000%20crore%20to%20Rs.6%2C799%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20employment%20challenge%20is%20as%20much%20about%20the%20scarcity%20of%20jobs%20as%20it%20is%20about%20the%20mismatch%20between%20skills%20and%20industry%20needs.%20It%20is%20uncertain%20if%20the%20government's%20skill%20development%20programmes%20are%20effective%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20corresponding%20private%20sector%20participation.%20And%20where%20are%20the%20jobs%20being%20generated%3F%20Employment%20creation%20cannot%20solely%20rely%20on%20government%20schemes%3B%20a%20thriving%20manufacturing%20sector%20and%20resilient%20MSME%20ecosystems%20are%20fundamental%20to%20long%20term%20job%20creation%E2%80%94yet%2C%20in%20a%20masterclass%20of%20misplaced%20priorities%2C%20the%20Budget%20has%20nothing%20for%20them%20but%20words.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMillions%20in%20rural%20India%20rely%20on%20MGNREGA%2C%20yet%20the%20scheme%20finds%20itself%20sidelined.%20The%20Finance%20Ministry%20has%20overlooked%20the%20%E2%82%B94%2C315%20crore%20shortfall%20in%20wages%20flagged%20by%20the%20Rural%20Development%20Ministry%2C%20while%20the%202024%20allocation%20remains%20stagnant%20at%20%E2%82%B986%2C000%20crore%E2%80%945%25%20lower%20than%202022%E2%80%9323%2C%20despite%20surging%20demand.%20With%20over%2082.4%20million%20seeking%20work%20under%20MGNREGA%2C%20this%20apathy%20is%20incomprehensible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Need%20To%20Focus%20On%20MSMEs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Budget%20speaks%20of%20making%20India%20a%20major%20global%20centre%20for%20the%20production%20of%20toys%20and%20bolstering%20the%20leather%20and%20footwear%20sectors.%20Nevertheless%2C%20there%20are%20no%20significant%20financial%20commitments%20to%20support%20these%20ambitious%20claims.%20These%20sectors%20receive%20the%20lowest%20allocation%20of%20any%20industry%20under%20the%20Production%20Linked%20Incentive%20(PLI)%20plan%2C%20a%20pitiful%20%E2%82%B90.01%20crore%20for%202024%E2%80%932025.%20Such%20statements%20remain%20empty%20rhetoric%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20real%20investments.%20Every%20Indian%20parent%20is%20swamped%20by%20%E2%80%9CMade%20in%20China%E2%80%9D%20toys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%2064%20million%20MSMEs%2C%20outnumbering%20those%20in%20China%20and%20the%20US%2C%20are%20the%20backbone%20of%20employment%20and%20entrepreneurship%E2%80%94yet%20remain%20largely%20neglected.%20With%20only%2014%25%20having%20access%20to%20credit%E2%80%94far%20below%20global%20peers%E2%80%94burdensome%20lending%20and%20minimal%20support%20stifle%20their%20growth.%20Credit%20guarantees%20alone%20won't%20bridge%20this%20gap%3B%20bold%20fiscal%20intervention%20is%20needed%20to%20unlock%20their%20full%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFiscal%20Deficit%20Concerns%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20remember%20the%20late%20Arun%20Jaitley%20announcing%20plans%20to%20bring%20the%20fiscal%20deficit%20down%20to%203%25%20will%20be%20underwhelmed%20by%20the%20present%20finance%20minister's%20intention%20to%20lower%20the%20budget%20deficit%20from%20the%20revised%204.8%25%20in%20FY25%20to%204.4%25%20in%20FY26.%20Concerns%20regarding%20fiscal%20planning%20are%20raised%20by%20the%20government's%20planned%20foregoing%20of%20%E2%82%B92%2C600%20crore%20in%20indirect%20taxes%20and%20%E2%82%B91%20lakh%20crore%20in%20direct%20tax%20revenue.%20However%2C%20this%20might%20lead%20to%20less%20expenditure%20by%20the%20government%2C%20which%20could%20have%20an%20effect%20on%20economic%20expansion.%20The%20government%20must%20make%20sure%20that%20vital%20welfare%20programmes%20are%20not%20sacrificed%20in%20the%20quest%20for%20a%20short-term%20feel-good%20headline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20FDI%20inflows%20have%20collapsed%20to%20just%20%240.48%20billion%20in%20the%20first%20eight%20months%20of%20FY25%2C%20down%20from%20%248.5%20billion%20in%20FY24%E2%80%94exposing%20deeper%20structural%20issues%20beyond%20external%20pressures.%20Investor%20confidence%20is%20eroding%20under%20the%20persistence%20of%20regulatory%20bottlenecks%2C%20policy%20unpredictability%2C%20and%20bureaucratic%20inertia.%20Without%20urgent%20reforms%20to%20cut%20red%20tape%20and%20restore%20stability%2C%20India%20risks%20deterring%20much-needed%20capital%20and%20long-term%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERising%20Medical%20Costs%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bmissing%20middle%26quot%3B%E2%80%9440%20crore%20Indians%E2%80%94remain%20without%20financial%20protection%20against%20medical%20costs%2C%20a%20glaring%20gap%20highlighted%20by%20NITI%20Aayog%20in%202021.%20While%20last%20year's%20expansion%20of%20PM-JAY%20to%20seniors%20was%20a%20step%20forward%2C%20this%20budget%20failed%20to%20build%20on%20that%20momentum.%20Millions%20remain%20uninsured%2C%20leaving%20them%20vulnerable%20to%20financial%20ruin%20from%20medical%20crises.%20Universal%20healthcare%20cannot%20be%20achieved%20through%20piecemeal%20efforts.%20The%20government%20must%20prioritise%20expanding%20coverage%2C%20combining%20direct%20aid%20for%20vulnerable%20groups%20with%20a%20public-private%20model%20that%20ensures%20affordable%20insurance%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUDAN's%20Slow%20Flight%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20significant%20announcement%20was%20the%20extension%20of%20the%20UDAN%20project%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20improve%20regional%20connectivity.%20It%20is%20admirable%20that%20UDAN%20will%20be%20expanded%20to%20120%20more%20locations%2C%20including%20small%20airports%20and%20helipads.%20A%20closer%20examination%20of%20the%20budgetary%20allocation%2C%20however%2C%20reveals%20a%20different%20picture.%20The%20Regional%20Connectivity%20Scheme%20has%20seen%20a%20steady%20decrease%20in%20funding%2C%20going%20from%20%E2%82%B91%2C063.81%20crore%20in%202022%E2%80%932023%20to%20%E2%82%B9502%20crore%20in%202024%E2%80%932025.%20Without%20sufficient%20funding%2C%20UDAN's%20long-term%20viability%20is%20still%20in%20doubt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20scheme's%20focus%20fails%20to%20address%20the%20pressing%20need%20to%20overcome%20under-served%20routes%20as%20opposed%20to%20merely%20aiding%20under-served%20airports.%20In%20important%20sectors%20like%20Trivandrum-Coimbatore%20and%20Trivandrum-Kochi-Kozhikode-Kannur%2C%20where%20flights%20are%20non-existent%20despite%20high%20demand%2C%20connectivity%20gaps%20still%20exist%20for%20which%20UDAN%20should%20be%20extended%20to%20resolve.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20budget's%20political%20cynicism%20was%20on%20full%20display%20with%20its%20multiple%20provisions%20for%20Bihar.%20Bihar%20is%20one%20of%20the%20states%20that%20legitimately%20needs%20investment%20in%20its%20development%2C%20but%20the%20disproportionate%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cnoutpouring%20of%20money%20has%20little%20to%20do%20with%20financial%20priorities%20and%20everything%20to%20do%20with%20the%20imminence%20of%20an%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EElections%20And%20Budgets%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElection%20strategy%20should%20not%20determine%20federal%20budgets%3B%20economic%20priorities%20should.%20Rather%20than%20favouring%20some%20states%20over%20others%20for%20political%20reasons%2C%20fiscal%20policy%20should%20be%20based%20on%20equitable%20growth%20and%20real%20development%20needs.%20Long-term%20vision%2C%20not%20short-term%20political%20calculations%2C%20must%20guide%20budgetary%20decisions%20if%20India%20is%20to%20maintain%20the%20integrity%20of%20its%20economic%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20political%20representative%2C%20I%20have%20to%20express%20my%20disappointment%20that%20Kerala's%20requests%E2%80%94ranging%20from%20funds%20for%20climate%20resilience%2C%20Wayanad's%20reconstruction%2C%20to%20an%20AIIMS-level%20facility%E2%80%94were%20given%20the%20go-by.%20%C2%A0The%20Union%20Budget's%20lack%20of%20proviso%20for%20Kerala%2C%20whose%20Vizhinjam%20Port%2C%20despite%20its%20strategic%20importance%2C%20received%20no%20support%E2%80%94further%20adds%20to%20the%20impression%20of%20systemic%20indifference%20to%20the%20state%20in%20fiscal%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20mounting%20hardships%2C%20the%20fishing%20community%20finds%20little%20relief%20in%20the%20budget%E2%80%94mentioned%20in%20passing%20but%20offered%20no%20real%20support.%20With%20depleting%20fish%20stocks%2C%20falling%20prices%2C%20and%20the%20removal%20of%20paraffin%20subsidies%20essential%20for%20boat%20fuel%2C%20thousands%20of%20fishermen%20face%20growing%20uncertainty.%20Yet%2C%20there%20is%20no%20financial%20aid%2C%20no%20relief%20package%2C%20no%20regulatory%20intervention%E2%80%94only%20indifference%20towards%20a%20community%20in%20crisis.%20Addressing%20these%20escalating%20issues%20requires%20an%20all-encompassing%20fisheries%20policy%20that%20includes%20sustainable%20resource%20management%2C%20financial%20assistance%2C%20and%20transformative%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Budget%202025%20introduces%20some%20commendable%20measures%2C%20its%20approach%20to%20Viksit%20Bharat%20feels%20more%20like%20a%20cautious%20shuffle%20than%20a%20confident%20stride.%20A%20truly%20developed%20India%20requires%20bold%2C%20forward-thinking%20investments%20in%20employment%2C%20MSMEs%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20infrastructure.%20For%20Viksit%20Bharat%20to%20be%20realised%2C%20the%20government%20must%20bridge%20the%20gap%20between%20aspiration%20and%20execution%2C%20ensuring%20that%20economic%20growth%20translates%20into%20real%20opportunities%20and%20inclusive%20progress%20for%20all.%20Did%20someone%20say%20%E2%80%9CSab%20ka%20saath%20sab%20ka%20vikas%E2%80%9D%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shashi%20Tharoor%20has%20been%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20from%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20Kerala%2C%20since%202009.%20He%20is%20a%20published%20author%20and%20a%20former%20diplomat.%20He%C2%A0thanks%20Urjaswi%20Ahlawat%20for%20her%20support%20in%20preparing%20this%20analysis.%20Inputs%20from%20my%20MP%20staff%20were%20invaluable.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%20and%20do%20not%20represent%20NDTV's%20views%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739433060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-03%2Fu6env2p_jobs-unemployment-reuters-_625x300_13_March_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Funion-budget-2025-balancing-act-or-missed-opportunity-7700213%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20Budget%202025%20introduces%20some%20commendable%20measures%2C%20its%20approach%20to%20Viksit%20Bharat%20feels%20more%20like%20a%20cautious%20shuffle%20than%20a%20confident%20stride.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Funion-budget-2025-balancing-act-or-missed-opportunity-7700213%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20unfollows%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%20after%20his%20controversy%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739432806000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118206981%2Cimgsize-44794.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fvirat-kohli-unfollows-ranveer-allahbadia-aka-beer-biceps-after-his-controversial-remark-the-internet-reacts-see-inside%2Farticleshow%2F118206990.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5