20aspersions%20on%20the%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20following%20a%20meeting%20between%20Opposition%20MPs%2C%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20and%20Union%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%2C%20a%20breakthrough%20was%20reached%20and%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20the%20dissent%20notes%20of%20Opposition%20members%20would%20be%20included%20in%20the%20JPC's%20draft%20report%20in%20their%20original%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20issue%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMany%20members%20have%20given%20their%20dissent%20note.%20Removing%20them%20from%20proceedings%20and%20keeping%20only%20the%20majority%20view%20is%20condemnable%20and%20anti-democracy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%2C%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20said%20there%20is%20no%20deletion.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20mislead%20the%20House%2C%20Opposition%20parties%20are%20making%20an%20unnecessary%20issue%2C%20the%20allegation%20is%20false%2C%20JPC%20conducted%20all%20proceedings%2C%20no%20rule%20was%20violated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rijiju%20later%20told%20the%20media%20that%20as%20per%20the%20rule%2C%20statements%20that%20%26quot%3Bamount%20to%20casting%20aspersions%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20committee%20can%20be%20deleted%20or%20removed%20by%20the%20chairman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Opposition%20MPs%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20walked%20out%20in%20protest%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20House%20JP%20Nadda%20said%20the%20Opposition%20did%20not%20want%20to%20discuss%20the%20issue%2C%20but%20score%20political%20points.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20has%20said%20nothing%20has%20been%20deleted.%20The%20Opposition%20has%20acted%20very%20irresponsibly.%20This%20is%20the%20politics%20of%20appeasement.%20The%20biggest%20question%20in%20question%20hour%20is%20that%20some%20people%20are%20trying%20to%20fight%20