%3A%22In%20This%20UP%20Wedding%2C%20Uninvited%20Guest%20Was%20A%20Leopard.%20What%20Happened%20Next%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20uninvited%20guest%20caused%20huge%20panic%20at%20a%20wedding%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Lucknow%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%20A%20leopard%20gate-crashed%20the%20wedding%20of%20Akshay%20Srivastava%20and%20Jyoti%20Kumari%2C%20forcing%20guests%20to%20run%20for%20their%20lives.%20The%20incident%20took%20place%20at%20the%20city's%20MM%20Lawn%20late%20last%20night%2C%20at%2011%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20wedding%20filled%20with%20love%2C%20joy%20and%20music%20suddenly%20transformed%20into%20a%20nightmare%20as%20the%20leopard%20trotted%20into%20the%20lit-up%20lawn.%20Within%20seconds%2C%20there%20were%20screams%20as%20guests%20ran%20out%20to%20the%20road.%20One%20guest%20jumped%20off%20the%20first%20floor%20of%20the%20venue%20and%20suffered%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bride%20and%20groom%20ran%20off%20and%20locked%20themselves%20in%20a%20car%2C%20an%20eyewitness%20said%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForest%20department%20officials%20and%20the%20police%20showed%20up%20after%20an%20SOS%20and%20then%20began%20a%20nearly%20five-hour-long%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leopard%20was%20finally%20found%20on%20the%20first%20floor%2C%20hiding%20in%20one%20of%20the%20rooms.%20As%20forest%20department%20official%20Muqaddar%20Ali%20approached%20the%20animal%2C%20it%20leapt%20and%20attacked%20him%20with%20its%20paw.%20The%20visuals%20show%20the%20forest%20officer's%20left%20hand%20covered%20in%20blood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20operation%20went%20on%20till%20the%20leopard%20was%20caught%20around%203%3A30%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20camerapersons%20also%20suffered%20injuries%20after%20they%20were%20knocked%20down%20in%20the%20mad%20scramble%20to%20escape%20the%20wedding%20venue%2C%20reports%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20unexpected%20overnight%20pause%2C%20the%20wedding%20rituals%20resumed%20the%20next%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739429580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F7auk6tc8_leopard-at-lucknow-wedding_625x300_13_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fleopard-gatecrashes-lucknow-wedding-bride-and-groom-lock-themselves-in-car-7699405%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Lucknow%20wedding%20filled%20with%20love%2C%20joy%20and%20music%2C%20had%20fear%20written%20all%20over%20it%20as%20a%20leopard%20was%20spotted%20on%20the%20marriage%20lawn.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fleopard-gatecrashes-lucknow-wedding-bride-and-groom-lock-themselves-in-car-7699405%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Modi%20In%20France%3A%20How%20Governance%20Will%20Be%20The%20'Killer'%20AI%20App%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20age%20of%20AI%20is%20here%20and%20we%20are%20living%20in%20the%20most%20exciting%20and%20transformative%20period%20in%20our%20lives.%20The%20Paris%20AI%20Action%20summit%20and%20the%20conversations%20there%20reiterate%20that.%C2%A0The%20summit%20was%20the%20third%20chapter%20since%20the%20UK%20launched%20the%20AI%20Safety%20Summit%20in%20November%202023%2C%20where%20I%20represented%20India.%20India%20was%20Co-Chair%20of%20this%20summit%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20himself%20attending%2C%20following%20our%20chairmanship%20of%20the%20December%202023%20New%20Delhi%20Global%20Partnership%20of%20AI%20summit%2C%20which%20he%20had%20inaugurated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20participation%20and%20co-chairing%20of%20this%20summit%20was%20very%20important%20and%20appropriate.%20India%20under%20PM%20Modi%20has%20become%20a%20global%20case%20study%20of%20how%20a%20country%20has%20used%20tech%20to%20transform%20itself%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20both%20governance%20and%20economy.%20India's%20Digital%20Public%20Infrastructure%20(DPI)%20has%20become%20a%20framework%20that%20countries%20around%20the%20world%20are%20adopting%20rapidly%20or%20aspiring%20to.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20DeepSeek%20Watershed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Paris%20AI%20summit%20was%20held%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20dramatic%20entry%20of%20China%20into%20the%20global%20AI%20scene%20with%20DeepSeek.%20The%20rapid%20progress%20made%20by%20AI%20since%20the%20launch%20of%20ChatGPT%20in%20late%202022%20was%20dominated%20more%20or%20less%20by%20US%20Tech%20giants%3A%20Open%20AI%2C%20Google%2C%20Meta%2C%20X%2C%20etc.%20The%20narrative%20in%20recent%20months%20has%20been%20built%20around%20these%20companies%20%2C%20their%20work%20and%20platforms%20in%20AI%20and%20their%20access%20to%20capital%20and%20AI%20compute%20infra%20that%20was%20helping%20them%20%E2%80%9Cscale%E2%80%9D.%20The%20dramatic%20entry%20of%20DeepSeek%20and%20its%20strategy%20to%20open-source%20its%20models%20has%20altered%20and%20broadened%20the%20narrative%20and%20discourse%20dramatically.%20That%20was%20apparent%20at%20the%20Paris%20Summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20three%20broad%20threads%20that%20dominated%20the%20conversations%20in%20Paris.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Progress%20Of%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%20was%20the%20original%20strand%20of%20the%20progress%20of%20AI%2C%20and%20the%20prediction%20of%20the%20roadmap%20to%20AGI%20(artifical%20general%20intelligence)%20and%20ASI%20(artificial%20superintelligence)%20and%20%E2%80%98singularity'.%20This%20has%20dominated%20the%20discourse%20around%20AI%20in%20the%20last%20year.%20This%20conversation%20has%20been%20tempered%20by%20the%20realisation%20that%20capital%20expenditure%20alone%20wasn't%20the%20moat%20that%20AI%20stalwarts%20like%20Sam%20Altman%20had%20anticipated.%20We%20were%20stepping%20into%20the%20next%20phase%20of%20AI%20where%20real%20research%20and%20innovation%20in%20algorithms%2C%20datasets%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20training%20and%20learning%20were%20going%20to%20be%20equally%20important%20in%20shaping%20the%20impact%2C%20success%20and%20quality%20of%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20models%20and%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernance%20Over%20Everything%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%20thread%20was%20one%20that%20India's%20presence%20and%20PM%20Modi's%20approach%20has%20triggered.%20Even%20while%20Big%20Tech%20giants%20are%20investing%20billions%20in%20general-purpose%20Large%20Language%20Models%20(LLMs)%20and%20applications%20on%20them%2C%20India's%20focus%20on%20AI%20being%20built%20for%20use%20cases%20in%20healthcare%2C%20education%2C%20agriculture%2C%20etc%2C%20has%20prompted%20the%20creation%20of%20killer%20apps%20for%20AI.%20Governance%20can%20be%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20areas%20where%20AI%20can%20make%20deep%2C%20very%20meaningful%20impacts.%20It%20was%20obvious%20that%20the%20momentum%20of%20conversations%20and%20discussions%20around%20real%20deployment%20of%20AI%20and%20success%20in%20use%20cases%20will%20be%20led%20by%20India.%20I%20attended%20a%20series%20of%20sessions%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20summit%2C%20arranged%20by%20the%20Tony%20Blair%20Institute%20and%20titled%20%E2%80%98Governing%20in%20the%20Age%20of%20AI'.%20I%20have%20written%20and%20spoken%20about%20this%20earlier.%20I%20am%20convinced%20that%20governance%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20killer%20app%20for%20AI%20and%20that%20India%20will%20demonstrate%20that%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Making%20AI%20'Responsible'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20thread%20that%20was%20discussed%20in%20Paris%20was%20about%20safe%20and%20trusted%20AI%20that%20would%20ensure%20only%20responsible%20and%20ethical%20use%20of%20AI.%20%C2%A0This%20is%20an%20area%20where%20there%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20really%20focused%20discussions%20on%20regulation%20and%20control%2C%20but%20also%20a%20lot%20of%20hot%20air%20and%20rhetoric.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWas%20AI%20to%20be%20regulated%20for%20harms%2Fbias%2Fcorrectness%2C%20or%20was%20it%20to%20be%20guardrails%20that%20platforms%20would%20follow%20voluntarily%3F%20%C2%A0What%20about%20how%20some%20countries%20like%20China%20had%20access%20to%20the%20global%20internet%20while%20shutting%20off%20its%20internet%20to%20any%20non-Chinese%20platforms%2C%20thus%20creating%20asymmetry%20of%20knowledge%20and%20data%3F%20%C2%A0What%20about%20open-source%20AI%20models%20vs%20closed%20AI%20models%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20all%20very%20foundational%20questions%20around%20the%20role%20of%20governments%20and%20public%20policy%20towards%20AI%20in%20specific%20and%20technology%20in%20General.%20Big%20Tech%20has%20for%20the%20last%20two%20decades%20more%20or%20less%20escaped%20regulation%20because%20%C2%A0they%20have%20argued%20they%20were%20innovators.%20There%20is%20a%20built-in%20resistance%20and%20pushback%20in%20technological%20companies%20towards%20any%20attempts%20by%20governments%20to%20regulate%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESafety%20And%20Trust%20Are%20Paramount%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESafety%20and%20trust%20take%20on%20a%20very%20significant%20meaning%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI.%20For%20a%20world%20that%20has%20struggled%20unsuccessfully%20with%20misinformation%2C%20disinformation%20and%20influence%20operations%20on%20social%20media%2C%20AI%20represents%20that%20problem%20to%20the%20power%20of%20infinity.%20India's%20position%20on%20this%20has%20been%20demonstrated%20by%20PM%20Modi's%20approach%20to%20data%20protection%2C%20which%20I%20explained%20in%20my%20interactions%20in%20Paris%E2%80%94that%20we%20don't%20consider%20citizen%20rights%20and%20innovation%20to%20be%20binaries%20that%20need%20to%20be%20balanced.%20Policymakers%20can%20ensure%20both%20if%20we%20look%20at%20this%20pragmatically%20and%20in%20a%20contemporary%20manner.%20That%20voluntary%20guidelines%20won't%20do%20and%20that%20we%20need%20a%20framework%20of%20laws%20that%20provide%20adaptive%20guardrails%20to%20prevent%20AI%20from%20causing%20harm%2C%20bias%2C%20falsehoods%20and%20criminality.%20AI%20available%20on%20the%20global%20internet%20must%20be%20safe%20and%20trusted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan't%20Deny%20Tech%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20experts%2C%20like%20Yoshua%20Bengio%20from%20University%20of%20Montreal%2C%20and%20others%20like%20OpenAI's%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20have%20argued%20against%20permitting%20open-source%20AI.%20Yoshua%20Bengio%20recently%20authored%20a%20huge%20400-page%20document%20of%20AI%20safety.%20Their%20main%20argument%20was%20that%20bad%20people%20will%20get%20access%20to%20AI%2C%20and%20that%20this%20can%20be%20prevented%20by%20keeping%20AI%20models%20closed.%20This%20of-course%20is%20a%20double-edged%20argument%20because%20it%20also%20normalises%20the%20notion%20that%20there%20should%20be%20only%20a%20few%20AI%20models%20owned%20by%20a%20few%20companies%2C%20and%20that%20everybody%20else%20will%20have%20to%20use%20those%20models.%20This%20construct%20is%20now%20contrary%20to%20the%20history%20of%20technology%2C%20where%20every%20proprietary%20system%20has%20been%20upended%20by%20the%20unrelenting%20and%20unstoppable%20force%20of%20innovation%20and%20innovators%20who%20disrupt%20the%20existing%20normal.%20%C2%A0DeepSeek%20has%20shown%20us%20that.%20There%20will%20be%20many%20more%20who%20will%20in%20coming%20months%20and%20years%20keep%20rewriting%20the%20normal%20of%20AI%20as%20we%20know%20it%20today.%20That%20is%20the%20real%20normal.%20So%2C%20open-source%20AI%20models%20are%20inevitable%2C%20and%20as%20I%20said%20in%20one%20of%20the%20sessions%20when%20asked%2C%20those%20who%20oppose%20open-source%20betray%20a%20lack%20of%20understanding%20of%20how%20technology%20has%20progressed%20and%20proliferated%20in%20contemporary%20times.%20That%20denial%20of%20technology%20has%20never%20worked%20in%20our%20times%E2%80%94not%20for%20missile%2C%20nor%20for%20nuclear%20bombs.%20It's%20definitely%20not%20going%20to%20work%20for%20software%20models%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20personally%2C%20these%20summits%20and%20the%20conversations%20with%20very%20bright%20minds%20are%20inspiring%20and%20exciting.%20I%20started%20my%20career%20as%20a%20tech%20geek%20coder%2C%20who%20through%20fate%20became%20a%20telecom%20entrepreneur%20and%20then%20a%20politician%20in%20public%20service.%20These%20summits%20reinforce%20that%20I%20remain%20a%20tech%20geek%20even%20today.%20I%20have%20been%20fortunate%20to%20have%20lived%20through%20the%20compute%2C%20internet%2C%20semiconductor%20disruptions%2C%20and%20am%20living%20now%20in%20the%20most%20exciting%20time%20ever%20in%20the%20history%20of%20tech%3A%20the%20AI%20Age.%20It's%20here.%20Get%20set%20for%20a%20transformative%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20the%20former%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%2C%20Skill%20Development%20and%20Entrepreneurship%20and%20Jal%20Shakti)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739429460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fi6gijtcs_pm-modi-ai-action-summit-afp_625x300_11_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffrance-ai-summit-let-india-show-the-way-on-governance-7699811%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Governance%20can%20be%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20areas%20where%20AI%20can%20make%20deep%2C%20very%20meaningful%20impacts.%20It%20was%20obvious%20that%20the%20momentum%20of%20conversations%20and%20discussions%20around%20real%20deployment%20of%20AI%20and%20success%20in%20use%20cases%20will%20be%20led%20by%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffrance-ai-summit-let-india-show-the-way-on-governance-7699811%22%2C%22cdnA