is%20the%20base%20of%20the%20pyramid%2C%20over%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20new%20recruits%20coming%20into%20our%20states%20are%20women.%20There%20are%20states%20where%20the%20recruitment%20of%20women%20goes%20up%20to%2060%20or%2070%20per%20cent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20higher%20judiciary%20now%20reflects%20the%20status%20of%20the%20legal%20profession%2010%20years%20ago.%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20happening%20now%2C%20as%20the%20reach%20of%20education%2C%20particularly%20legal%20education%2C%20has%20reached%20women%2C%20that%20gender%20balance%20you%20find%20in%20law%20schools%20is%20now%20reflected%20in%20the%20lowest%20levels%20of%20indian%20judiciary.%20In%20so%20far%20as%20gender%20balance%20in%20concerned%2C%20you%20find%20an%20increasing%20number%20of%20women%20coming%20into%20district%20judiciary%20and%20these%20women%20will%20be%20climbing%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20question%20about%20being%20the%20son%20of%20a%20Chief%20Justice%2C%20he%20said%20that%20his%20father%2C%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20YV%20Chandrachud%2C%20had%20told%20him%20not%20to%20enter%20a%20court%20of%20law%20so%20long%20as%20he%20was%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20I%20spent%20three%20years%20at%20Harvard%20Law%20School%20doing%20my%20studies.%20I%20entered%20a%20court%20for%20the%20first%20time%20after%20he%20retired.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20the%20overall%20profile%20of%20the%20Indian%20judiciary%2C%20most%20lawyers%20and%20judges%20are%20first-time%20entrants%20into%20the%20legal%20profession.%20So%20quite%20contrary%20to%20what%20you%20said%2C%20it%20is%20not%20that%20our%20judiciary%20is%20either%20upper%20caste%20or...%20in%20the%20higher%20echelons%20of%20judiciary%2C%20the%20movement%20of%20women%20to%20more%20responsible%20positions%20is%20just%20about%20taking%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FtH3hUlbiJs4%3Fsi%3D83i-07g49ux1uclM%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPressure%20From%20Modi%20Government%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20was%20asked%20if%20he%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20political%20pressure%20during%20his%20term.%20Mr%20Sackur%20quoted%20an%20editorial%20in%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20which%20said%20that%20according%20to%20political%20opponents%2C%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20had%20leaned%20on%20the%20courts%20to%20protect%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20(retd)%20Chandrachud%20said%20the%202024%20general%20election%20results%20debunked%20the%20myth%20that%20India%20is%20combining%20towards%20a%20one-party%20state.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20states%20in%20India%2C%20the%20states%20are%20where%20the%20regional%20aspirations%20and%20identities%20have%20come%20to%20the%20fore%2C%20and%20so%20many%20of%20our%20states%20in%20India%20you%20have%20regional%20political%20parties%20which%20have%20done%20exceptionally%20well%20and%20they%20are%20ruling%20those%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20conviction%20in%20a%20defamation%20case%2C%20he%20said%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20later%20paused%20the%20judgment.%20Citing%20the%20number%20of%20people%20who%20have%20been%20granted%20bail%2C%20many%20of%20them%20political%20leaders%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHigher%20courts%2C%20particularly%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20have%20sent%20a%20clear%20message%20that%20we%20are%20here%20to%20safeguard%20personal%20liberties%2C%20in%20individual%20cases%2C%20there%20may%20be%20a%20difference%20of%20personal%20opinion%2C%20but%20the%20fact%20of%20the%20matter%20is%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20been%20at%20the%20vanguard%20of%20personal%20liberty.%20This%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20we%20have%20the%20faith%20of%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArticle%20370%20Judgment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sackur%20told%20the%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20that%20many%20legal%20scholars%20were%20disappointed%20with%20the%20top%20court's%20judgment%20in%20the%20Article%20370%20case%20which%20had%20challenged%20the%20Centre's%20move%20to%20revoke%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20special%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20I%20was%20the%20author%20of%20one%20of%20the%20judgments%20in%20the%20case%2C%20a%20judge%20by%20the%20very%20nature%20of%20their%20profession%20has%20some%20restraints%20on%20defending%20or%20critiquing%20their%20judgments.%20I%20will%20briefly%20answer%20your%20question%20notwithstanding%20my%20caveat.%20Article%20370%20when%20it%20was%20introduced%20into%20the%20Constitution%20was%20part%20of%20a%20chapter%20which%20is%20titled%20Transitional%20Arrangements%2C%20it%20was%20later%20renamed%20Temporary%20and%20Transitional%20Arrangements.%20Therefore%20at%20the%20birth%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20assumption%20was%20that%20what%20was%20transitional%20would%20have%20to%20fade%20away%20and%20merge%20with%20the%20overall%20context%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20Is%2075%20plus%20years%20too%20less%20for%20abrogating%20a%20transitional%20provision%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20(retd)%20Chandrachud%20said%20the%20democratic%20process%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20must%20be%20restored%20and%20a%20democratically%20elected%20government%20is%20in%20place%20now.%20%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20a%20peaceful%20transfer%20of%20power%20to%20a%20government%20which%20is%20a%20political%20party%20which%20is%20not%20of%20the%20dispensation%20as%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20Delhi.%20This%20is%20a%20clear%20indicator%20that%20democracy%20has%20succeeded%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20statehood%20question%2C%20he%20said%20the%20government%20had%20given%20an%20undertaking%20that%20the%20status%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20would%20be%20restored%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20%26quot%3BTherefore%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20ensured%20democratic%20accountability%2C%20a%20people's%20government%20is%20in%20place%2C%20so%20the%20criticism%20that%20we%20didn't%20apply%20our%20Constitutional%20mandate%20is%20not%20correct%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20CAA%20Question%2C%20A%20UK%20Jab%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Sackur%20asked%20Justice%20(retd)%20Chandrachud%20about%20the%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20and%20why%20it%20was%20not%20taken%20up%20during%20his%20term%2C%20he%20replied%20that%20the%20case%20is%20pending%20and%20added%20a%20UK%20example.%20%26quot%3BIf%20this%20were%20to%20take%20place%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20the%20court%20would%20have%20no%20power%20to%20invalidate%20it.%20In%20India%2C%20we%20have%20the%20power%20to%20invalidate%20legislation%2C%20I%20wrote%20about%2062%20judgments%20for%20the%20Constitution%20bench%20through%20my%20tenure%2C%20we%20had%20constitutional%20cases%20which%20were%20pending%20for%2020%20years%2C%20dealing%20with%20critical%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20said%20he%20needed%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20old%20cases%20and%20new%20cases.%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20take%20up%20new%20cases%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20cases%2C%20or%20do%20you%20also%20deal%20with%20seminal%20old%20cases%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20did%20manage%20to%20dispose%20of%20a%20fair%20share%20of%20old%20cases%20too.%20The%20CAA%20case%2C%20he%20said%2C%20would%20be%20dealt%20with%20in%20due%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERam%20Temple%20Judgment%2C%20And%20Deity%20Remark%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20his%20purported%20remark%20that%20he%20sat%20before%20a%20deity%20before%20the%20landmark%20Ram%20Temple%20judgment%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20social%20media%20and%20try%20and%20derive%20what%20was%20said%20by%20a%20judge%2C%20you%20will%20get%20the%20wrong%20answer.%20I%20make%20no%20bones%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20am%20a%20man%20of%20faith%2C%20our%20Constitution%20does%20not%20require%20you%20to%20be%20an%20atheist%20to%20be%20an%20independent%20judge%2C%20and%20I%20value%20my%20faith%2C%20what%20my%20faith%20teaches%20me%20is%20the%20universality%20of%20religion%20and%20irrespective%20of%20who%20comes%20to%20my%20court%2C%20and%20that%20applies%20to%20all%20other%20judges%20in%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20you%20dispense%20equal%20and%20even-handed%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudges%20work%20in%20areas%20of%20conflict%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWithin%20that%20area%20of%20conflict%2C%20how%20do%20you%20find%20a%20sense%20of%20calm%2C%20of%20equanimity%2C%20different%20judges%20have%20different%20ways%20to%20approach%20that%20need%20for%20calm%20and%20equanimity.%20For%20me%2C%20time%20in%20meditation%20and%20prayer%20is%20very%20important%2C%20but%20my%20time%20in%20meditation%20and%20prayer%20teaches%20me%20to%20be%20even-handed%20to%20every%20religious%20group%20and%20community%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Prime%20Minister's%20Visit%20To%20His%20Home%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20the%20then%20Chief%20Justice's%20home%20for%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi%20had%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row%2C%20with%20several%20Opposition%20leaders%20making%20critical%20remarks.%20Asked%20about%20the%20issue%2C%20Justice%20(retd)%20Chandrachud%20said%20not%20much%20should%20be%20made%20out%20of%20%26quot%3Belementary%20courtesies%20of%20Constitutional%20office%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20our%20system%20is%20mature%20enough%20to%20understand%20that%20elementary%20courtesies%20which%20are%20observed%20between%20high%20Constitutional%20functionaries%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20way%20they%20dispose%20of%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20said%20before%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20visit%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20delivered%20judgments%20like%20in%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20case%20and%20after%20the%20visit%20too%2C%20it%20has%20delivered%20numerous%20judgments%20against%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20role%20of%20the%20judiciary%20in%20a%20democratic%20society%20is%20not%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20parliament.%20We%20are%20here%20to%20decide%20cases%20and%20act%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739428020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F5r8qk31o_ex-cji-dy-chandrachud_625x300_13_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-chief-justice-dy-chandrachud-indian-judiciary-dominated-by-elite-hindu-male-ex-chief-justice-replies-7699693%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Higher%20courts%20in%20India%2C%20especially%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20has%20sent%20a%20clear%20message%20that%20we%20are%20here%20to%20safeguard%20personal%20liberties%20and%20that's%20why%20the%20judiciary%20has%20the%20faith%20of%20the%20people%2C%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-chief-justice-dy-chandrachud-indian-judiciary-dominated-by-elite-hindu-male-ex-chief-justice-replies-7699693%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Captain%20America%2C%20Chhaava%20%26amp%3B%20more%3A%20This%20week's%20releases%22%2C%22co