as%20a%20high%20school%20teacher%20for%20Barbers%20Hill%20ISD%20from%20August%202021%20to%20June%202023.%20She%20resigned%20earlier%20this%20month%26quot%3B%C2%A0%20a%20district%20spokesperson%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpears'%20attorney%2C%20Christopher%20L.%20Tritico%2C%20said%20that%20he%20is%20unsure%20why%20the%20case%20took%20over%20a%20year%20to%20move%20forward%2C%20but%20stated%20that%20his%20client%20is%20eager%20to%20contest%20the%20allegations%20against%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMs.%20Spears%20was%20first%20notified%20of%20the%20charges%20two%20days%20ago%20and%20we%20acted%20immediately%20to%20get%20the%20bond%20set%20up%20and%20in%20place.%20I%20cannot%20speak%20to%20why%20it%20sat%20so%20dormant%20for%20so%20long.%20That%20is%20a%20question%20for%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20aisle.%20Ms%20Spears%20looks%20forward%20to%20having%20an%20opportunity%20to%20confront%20the%20allegations%20and%20to%20finally%20put%20this%20matter%20behind%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tritico%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpears%20was%20hired%20by%20Barbers%20Hill%20ISD%20in%202021.%20She%20previously%20worked%20for%C2%A0Texas%20City%20ISD%20from%202014%20to%202020%2C%20and%C2%A0Coldspring%20ISD%20from%202012%20to%202014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disturbing%20phenomenon%20of%20teachers%20engaging%20in%20illegal%20sexual%20relationships%20with%20students%20is%20a%20growing%20concern%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20According%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ferretly.com%2Fblog%2Fteacher-student-sexual-misconduct-the-critical-role-of-social-media-screening%5C%22%3Erecent%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20were%20over%20500%20reported%20cases%20of%20teacher%20misconduct%20between%202014%20and%202019%2C%20with%20nearly%201%20in%2010%20students%20experiencing%20some%20form%20of%20sexual%20misconduct%20by%20an%20educator.%20Several%20factors%20contribute%20to%20this%20alarming%20trend%2C%20including%20increased%20reporting%20and%20awarene