%20the%20sixth%20day.%20Reviews%20were%20mostly%20negative.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fbadass-ravikumar-box-office-collection-day-6-himesh-reshammiyas-action-parody-maintains-steady-business-close-to-first-week-completion%2Farticleshow%2F118201011.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22For%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Cops%2C%20New%20Criminal%20Code%20Leads%20To%20A%20Pendrive%20Problem%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20unusual%20financial%20strain%2C%20police%20stations%20across%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20have%20been%20spending%20thousands%20of%20rupees%20on%20pen%20drives%20every%20month.%20The%20reason%3F%20A%20new%20legal%20mandate%20under%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20(BNS)%20requires%20all%20case-related%20evidence%20-%20statements%2C%20crime%20scene%20recordings%2C%20and%20forensic%20data%20-%20to%20be%20submitted%20in%20a%20pen%20drive%2C%20and%20not%20through%20CDs%20or%20paper%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20digitisation%20aims%20to%20streamline%20legal%20proceedings%2C%20the%20burden%20of%20purchasing%20these%20storage%20devices%20has%20landed%20squarely%20on%20the%20shoulders%20of%20police%20personnel%2C%20who%20often%20find%20themselves%20paying%20out%20of%20their%20own%20pockets.%20With%20an%208GB%20pen%20drive%20costing%20roughly%20around%20%E2%82%B9300%2C%20and%20investigations%20often%20requiring%20multiple%20devices%2C%20the%20change%20in%20norm%20has%20become%20a%20source%20of%20concern%20across%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BYou%20Have%20to%20Do%20It%2C%20Sir!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESub-Inspector%20BS%20Kalpuria%20at%20Bhopal's%20Kotwali%20Police%20Station%20has%20been%20serving%20for%20years%20and%20now%20investigates%20multiple%20cases%20under%20the%20new%20law.%20But%20the%20shift%20from%20paper%20to%20digital%20evidence%20has%20come%20at%20an%20unexpected%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20case%20requires%20at%20least%20three%20pen%20drives%20to%20put%20together%20the%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20do%20it%2C%20sir!%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kalpuria%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Digital%20Shift%20-%20An%20Expensive%20Affair%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Section%2065B(4)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%2C%20any%20electronic%20evidence%2C%20including%20pen%20drives%2C%20must%20come%20with%20a%20certificate%20verifying%20its%20authenticity.%20Previously%2C%20CDs%20were%20used%2C%20but%20they%20have%20become%20difficult%20to%20find%20and%20use%2C%20forcing%20police%20to%20switch%20to%20pen%20drives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Nagrik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20(BNSS)%20of%202023%20has%20provisions%20for%20recording%20evidence%20through%20audio-visual%20means.%20This%20includes%20recording%20crime%20scenes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20BNS%2C%20particularly%20Section%20105%2C%20evidence%20collected%20during%20a%20search%20and%20seizure%20operation%20must%20be%20recorded%20via%20audio-video%20electronic%20means%2C%20like%20a%20mobile%20phone%2C%20and%20stored%20on%20a%20device%20like%20a%20pen%20drive%2C%20essentially%20making%20the%20pen%20drive%20a%20medium%20to%20present%20the%20recorded%20evidence%20in%20court%3B%20this%20is%20mandated%20to%20ensure%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20in%20the%20investigation%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstable%20Pushpendra%20Prajapati%20echoed%20the%20struggle%3A%20%26quot%3BEarlier%2C%20CDs%20worked%20fine%2C%20but%20now%20we%20have%20to%20buy%20pen%20drives.%20Sometimes%2C%20we%20have%20to%20pay%20from%20our%20own%20salary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstable%20Joginder%20Singh%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BAt%20least%20three%20pen%20drives%20are%20required%20per%20case%2C%20costing%20between%20%E2%82%B9500-%E2%82%B9600.%20Right%20now%2C%20we're%20managing%20from%20our%20own%20pockets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECase%20Files%20on%20Pen%20Drives%3A%20A%20Costly%20Change%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESub-Inspector%20Prem%20Narayan%20(30)%20acknowledged%20the%20administrative%20burden.%20%26quot%3BEach%20case%20requires%20a%20minimum%20of%20two%20pen%20drives%20-%20one%20for%20the%20court%20and%20one%20for%20our%20records.%20If%20the%20accused's%20lawyer%20demands%20a%20copy%2C%20we%20need%20a%20third.%20We%20buy%20them%20ourselves%20because%20evidence%20collection%20is%20our%20responsibility%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20July%201%2C%202024%2C%20every%20police%20station%20has%20had%20to%20purchase%20its%20own%20pen%20drives%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Each%20time%20a%20case%20is%20registered%2C%20the%20victim's%20and%20witnesses'%20statements%20are%20recorded%20on%20video%20and%20stored%20in%20a%20pen%20drive%2C%20which%20is%20then%20presented%20in%20court%20along%20with%20all%20case%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETop%20Cop%20Acknowledges%20Shortage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhopal%20Police%20Commissioner%20Harinarayanchari%20Mishra%20admitted%20a%20resource%20constraint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BResources%20are%20being%20arranged%2C%20but%20initially%2C%20some%20police%20stations%20may%20face%20difficulties.%20The%20process%20of%20procuring%20equipment%20is%20ongoing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELegal%20professionals%20said%20the%20police%20should%20not%20have%20to%20bear%20this%20financial%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20advocate%20Rajendra%20Upadhyay%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20police%20are%20struggling%20because%20they%20lack%20a%20formal%20budget%20for%20pen%20drives.%20Yet%2C%20all%20evidence%20must%20now%20be%20submitted%20electronically.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERetired%20DGP%20SC%20Tripathi%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20pen%20drives%20were%20made%20mandatory%2C%20arrangements%20should%20have%20been%20in%20place.%20The%20government%20spends%20crores%20on%20welfare%20schemes%20like%20'Ladli%20Behna%2C'%20yet%20police%20stations%20don't%20have%20funds%20for%20a%20%E2%82%B9300%20pen%20drive!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20report%20revealed%20that%20between%20July%201%20and%20September%203%2C%202024%2C%205%2C56%2C000%20FIRs%20were%20registered%20under%20the%20new%20penal%20code%20-%20an%20average%20of%207%2C400%20FIRs%20per%20day.%20At%20this%20rate%2C%20police%20stations%20across%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20alone%20would%20need%20to%20spend%20%E2%82%B925%20lakh%20every%20month%20on%20pen%20drives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETechnology%20is%20making%20legal%20proceedings%20more%20efficient%20but%20the%20cost%20of%20implementation%20has%20clearly%20caught%20law%20enforcement%20off%20guard.%20Until%20the%20government%20formally%20allocates%20a%20budget%20for%20this%2C%20policemen%20will%20continue%20to%20foot%20the%20bill%20for%20their%20own%20investigations%20-%20one%20pen%20drive%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739420340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fvshshnmg_madhya-pradesh-police-pen-drive_625x300_11_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffor-madhya-pradesh-cops-new-criminal-code-leads-to-a-pendrive-problem-7688854%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20unusual%20financial%20strain%2C%20police%20stations%20across%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20have%20been%20spending%20thousands%20of%20rupees%20on%20pen%20drives%20every%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffor-madhya-pradesh-cops-new-criminal-code-leads-to-a-pendrive-problem-7688854%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Toy%20Train%2C%20Alphabet%20Set%3A%20PM%20Modi's%20Gifts%20For%20US%20Veep%20JD%20Vance's%20Children%22%2C%22cont