20Centre%20of%20Middle%20East%20Studies%20and%20the%20Farzaneh%20Family%20Center%20for%20Iranian%20and%20Persian%20Gulf%20Studies%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Oklahoma%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20easier%20chip%20in%20bargaining%20could%20be%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-special-operations-base-al-tanf-syria-iran-israel-war-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20base%20at%20al-Tanf%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Syria's%20southern%20desert.%20Controlled%20by%20the%20US-allied%2C%20anti-ISIS%20Syrian%20Free%20Army%20group%2C%20the%20base%20is%20situated%20near%20the%20Jordanian%20border%20and%20the%20important%20Baghdad-Damascus%20highway.%20The%20US%20enforced%20a%2034-mile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crisisgroup.org%2Ftrigger-list%2Firan-usisrael-trigger-list%2Fflashpoints%2Fal-tanf-syria%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ede-confliction%20zone%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20al-Tanf%20which%20Iranian-backed%20forces%20and%20Assad's%20regime%20weren't%20allowed%20to%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20presence%20at%20al-Tanf%20was%20pretty%20dubious%20before%20Assad%20fell%20and%20it%20serves%20no%20discernible%20purpose%20now%2C%20except%20possibly%20as%20a%20point%20of%20leverage%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20the%20new%20Damascus%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Aron%20Lund%2C%20Middle%20East%20analyst%20with%20the%20Swedish%20Defence%20Research%20Agency%20and%20fellow%20with%20Century%20International%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20al-Tanf%20could%20be%20a%20place%20they'll%20withdraw%20from%20first%2C%20perhaps%20after%20getting%20some%20little%20thing%20in%20return%20from%20Sharaa's%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SDF-controlled%20regions%20present%20a%20%26quot%3Bthornier%20issue%26quot%3B%20with%20much%20higher%20stakes.%20The%20Kurds%20guard%20prisons%20with%20thousands%20of%20ISIS%20fighters%2C%20but%20they'd%20be%20hard-pressed%20to%20maintain%20these%20faced%20with%20a%20major%20offensive