6quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225277%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20of%20the%20bedrooms%20at%20the%20resort.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679885417bb3f854015a989a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223981%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt's%20very%20different%20from%20the%20corporate%20life%20that%20she%20was%20used%20to.%3Cp%3ELubihan%20Siargao.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20says%20that%20her%20background%20working%20in%20an%20office%20taught%20her%20to%20be%20disciplined%2C%20which%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20helped%20her%20greatly%20in%20managing%20the%20hotel%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20she%20really%20appreciates%20about%20life%20in%20Siargao%20is%20the%20tight%20community%20on%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20you%20live%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Manila%2C%20you%20probably%20will%20not%20know%20your%20neighbor.%20In%20Siargao%2C%20everybody%20just%20talks%20to%20each%20other%2C%20which%20is%20very%2C%20very%20nice%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221366%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20garden.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a2fd0cbfebcc4d029dca29%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShe%20loves%20the%20tight%20community%20on%20the%20island.%3Cp%3ELubihan%20Siargao.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20she%20does%20occasionally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-left-nyc-tiny-house-farm-wont-do-it-again-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emiss%20city-living%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20convenience%20that%20comes%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20a%20fast%20food%20chain%20on%20the%20island.%20It's%20both%20good%20and%20bad%2C%20because%20sometimes%20you%20have%20cravings%20for%20a%20burger%2C%26quot%3B%20Ganaden%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20infra