dit%20card%2C%20which%20has%20a%20%24395%20annual%20fee.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Payne%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Capital%20One%20Venture%20X%20Rewards%20card%20certainly%20falls%20under%20the%20premium%20rewards%20card%20category%2C%20with%20an%20expensive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fhow-to-decide-if-credit-card-annual-fee-worth-it%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannual%20fee%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20%24395.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20my%20family%20justifies%20the%20bulk%20of%20this%20fee%20by%20taking%20full%20advantage%20of%20one%20of%20the%20card's%20most%20valuable%20perks%3A%20a%20%24300%20annual%20travel%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20cardholder%2C%20I%20receive%20a%20%24300%20credit%20each%20year%20for%20travel%20booked%20through%20Capital%20One%20Travel.%20We've%20had%20great%20luck%20booking%20rental%20vehicles%20through%20Capital%20One.%20And%20I%20have%20a%20flight%20booked%20through%20Capital%20One%20for%20an%20upcoming%20business%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22038ab508-d6a9-4264-91f8-dab49aa91320%5C%22%3EUsing%20a%20single%20credit%20card%20isn't%20for%20everybody%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20earning%20a%20decent%20flat%20rate%20on%20all%20of%20our%20spending%2C%20we%20no%20doubt%20leave%20valuable%20rewards%20on%20the%20table%20by%20only%20using%20the%20Capital%20One%20Venture%20X%20Rewards%20card.%20We%20realize%20that%2C%20but%20don't%20apologize%20for%20it%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20other%20credit%20cards%20and%20could%20earn%20more%20by%20rotating%20them%20for%20different%20types%20of%20expenses%2C%20but%20we'd%20rather%20spend%20that%20energy%20elsewhere.%20Anyone%20who%20claims%20that%20tracking%20spending%20categories%2C%20bonus%20rates%20and%20offers%2C%20annual%20credits%2C%20and%20other%20card%20features%20isn't%20that%20much%20work%20has%20superpowers%20I%20don't%20possess.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20some%20point%2C%20we'll%20transition%20back%20to%20using%20multiple%20credit%20cards%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20high%20bonus%20rates%20across%20a%20wider%20range%20of%20spending%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20family%20has%20several%20milestone%20events%20coming%20up%20in%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20and%20we're%20gearing%20up%20for%20increased%20travel%20during%20that%20period%2C%20so%20it%20would%20make%20sense%20to%20consider%20spreading%20our%20spending%20across%20specific%20types%20of%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20much%20as%20I%20enjoy%20earning%20as%20many%20rewards%20as%20possible%2C%20my%20time%20is%20better%20spent%20on%20other%20pursuits%20during%20this%20current%20season%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-i-use-one-credit-card-for-everything-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739400312000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a22920bfebcc4d029dac6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-i-use-one-credit-card-for-everything-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Adopting%20a%20one-card%20strategy%20with%20this%20premium%20credit%20card%20allows%20this%20family%20of%20six%20to%20travel%20in%20style%20with%20airport%20lounge%20access%20and%20easy%20rewards.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kevin%40familymoneyadventure.com%20(Kevin%20Payne)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-i-use-one-credit-card-for-everything-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20India%20fails%20to%20protect%20its%20domestic%20workers%20despite%20decades%20of%20abuse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739398692000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F62de%2Flive%2F71e957f0-e909-11ef-a9c1-a53be0633d50.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com